STS attempt #2
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Let's try it differently.
 Add and subtract to LHS identity matrix, such that we have
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
(\Gamma_{\alpha\beta}-M_{\alpha\beta}+\delta_{\alpha\beta})q_{\alpha}^{i}=q_{\beta}^{i}+\theta_{\beta}(0)q_{0}^{i}+\lambda\omega_{\beta}(q_{\beta}^{i+1}-2q_{\beta}^{i}+q_{\beta}^{i-1})
\]

\end_inset

 which gives us the following expansion 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\Lambda_{\alpha\beta}=\Gamma_{\alpha\beta}-M_{\alpha\beta}+\delta_{\alpha\beta}=\left(\begin{array}{cc}
\\
\\
\end{array}\right)
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

